{
  "stem": "25114.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're light-- and we were very, you know-- locked in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was very good for winter, because we got into-- this was coming December and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we decided to go into the winter zemlyankas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember going on foot-- it was quite a fair bit from the last place to this place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went into the zemlyankas, and we organized ourselves, and we stayed there for a little while.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day somebody-- and there was about four of them-- two in one place, and two in another place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one empty one, just in case somebody gets sick, you know-- to isolate him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was all prepared before I came to the triad, to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we went into those zemlyankas the way and-- we arrived, and had a look, and we decided that's it, you know.We go in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were there for about two months-- or six weeks or seven weeks, I can't remember-- from December to February.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody went to-- to get some supplies, some food, and they killed-- I don't remember-- a chicken or a pig or something, and they didn't drain it from the blood, and they had the whole-- a whole-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] prints-- the print-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- The trail?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trail, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The trail led right to our places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, not soon after, they attacked us-- the base.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or the police-- the local police, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They attacked us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They followed the trail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had good intelligence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Good [NON-ENGLISH], they were called-- good people what watched.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was two rows-- first was about a kilometer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there was time to tell us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
